      <title>印度 Piramal Pharma 计划五年内实现收入翻番</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-s-piramal-pharma-targets-doubling-revenue-in-five-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皮拉马尔制药有限公司 (Piramal Pharma Ltd.) 董事长南迪尼·皮拉马尔 (Nandini Piramal) 表示，该公司预计新分子开发和位于肯塔基州的无菌注射剂设施 8000 万美元的扩建将为其实现未来五年收入翻番的目标提供支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-s-piramal-pharma-targets-doubling-revenue-in-five-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 07:05:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
